OL,3,CMan given months to live becomes
OL,4,Cinvincible cricket captain
OL,6,FA Swansea business owner, who was told
OL,7,Fhe had just months to live after the
OL,8,Fdiscovery of a brain tumour, has
OL,9,Fbeaten the odds to captain his local
OL,10,Fcricket side through an unbeaten
OL,11,Fseason.
OL,13,FRobert Jones says a surgeon gave him
OL,14,Fbetween 12 and 18 months to live after
OL,15,Fhe underwent an operation to remove
OL,16,Fthe aggressive tumour.
