OL,3,CMan given months to live becomes
OL,4,Cinvincible cricket captain
OL,6,FThe 62-year-old owner of Rowberry shoe
OL,7,Fstores received immunotherapy
OL,8,Ftreatment at a hospital in London in
OL,9,FDecember 2022, where a vaccine was
OL,10,Fmade from his tumour, which he is
OL,11,Fstill using as treatment to prolong
OL,12,Fhis life.
OL,14,F"I was asymptomatic, so I had no idea
OL,15,Fwhat was coming", he told ITV Wales.
OL,17,F"It was coming to the end of the day,
OL,18,Fand I was looking forward to meeting
OL,19,Fup with friends, but I passed out and
OL,20,Fhad a seizure."
