OL,3,CMan given months to live becomes
OL,4,Cinvincible cricket captain
OL,6,F"Within a week, I was in the
OL,7,FUniversity Hospital of Wales, I was
OL,8,Foperated on, and a small tumour the
OL,9,Fsize of a marble was removed from the
OL,10,Fback of my head."
OL,12,FRobert says the prognosis after the
OL,13,Foperation was hard to take, with the
OL,14,Fsurgeon who had operated on him
OL,15,Ftelling him he had less than two years
OL,16,Fto live.
OL,18,F"The first thing I said to the surgeon
OL,19,Fwas, 'Are there any exceptions?' And
OL,20,Fshe said yes, it's about five per cent.
