OL,3,CMan given months to live becomes
OL,4,Cinvincible cricket captain
OL,6,F"I thought I am going to be that 5 per
OL,7,Fcent. I was determined from the word
OL,8,Fgo, I was going to beat it."
OL,10,FTwo and a half years on from his
OL,11,Foperation, Robert says the cancer is
OL,12,Funder control and he is feeling fit
OL,13,Fand well.
OL,15,FHe regularly captains Swansea Civil
OL,16,FService Cricket Club's third team and
OL,17,Flast year led the side through an
OL,18,Finvincible league season.
