OL,6,F"It's been over two and a half years,
OL,7,Fand I am still here. I'd like to think
OL,8,Fthe vaccines have given me a bit more
OL,9,Ftime, and I am feeling great. I'm
OL,10,Fplaying cricket every weekend, which
OL,11,Fis what I live for, so it's all
OL,12,Fpositive."
